{"sn36.2:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 36.2 ","sn36.2:0.2":"1. Sagathavagga ","sn36.2:0.3":"Sukhasutta ","sn36.2:1.1":"“Tisso ima, bhikkhave, vedana. ","sn36.2:1.2":"Katama tisso? ","sn36.2:1.3":"Sukha vedana, dukkha vedana, adukkhamasukha vedana—","sn36.2:1.4":"ima kho, bhikkhave, tisso vedanati. ","sn36.2:2.1":"Sukham va yadi va dukkham, ","sn36.2:2.2":"adukkhamasukham saha; ","sn36.2:2.3":"Ajjhattanca bahiddha ca, ","sn36.2:2.4":"yam kinci atthi veditam. ","sn36.2:3.1":"Etam dukkhanti natvana, ","sn36.2:3.2":"mosadhammam palokinam; ","sn36.2:3.3":"Phussa phussa vayam passam, ","sn36.2:3.4":"evam tattha virajjati”ti. ","sn36.2:3.5":"Dutiyam. "}